Class Farm

java.lang.Object
gamePackage.Farm
Direct Known Subclasses:
DesertFarm, MountainFarm, PlainsFarm, SwampFarm
public class Farm
extends java.lang.Object
Contains methods for adding/removing farm animals and money Also contains the farm's animal list, and crop list
Author:
Swapnil Bhagat, Reed Earl
